data.description:
Step into the perfect mix of comfort and luxury at 76 Windsong Loop, an enchanting 4 BR, 2.5 BA residence nestled within the sought after Redland area of Wetumpka, Alabama. Located within the coveted Windsong subdivision, this exquisite home offers not only unparalleled comfort and style but also exclusive access to a community pool, offering endless hours of relaxation and enjoyment throughout your summer. As you approach this property, you're greeted by the vibrant blooms that adorn the entry way. Sunlight pours in through the large windows, illuminating the open-concept living spaces. The heart of the home lies in the gourmet kitchen, where culinary dreams come to life amidst modern appliances, sleek countertops, and ample cabinet space.
Retreat to the luxurious master suite, where serenity awaits. Here, you'll find a spacious bedroom adorned with elegant finishes and a spa-like ensuite bathroom complete with a soaking tub, separate shower, and dual vanities, offering the ultimate in comfort and convenience. Three additional bedrooms offer ample space for family, guests, or a dedicated home office, ensuring flexibility to suit your unique needs and preferences. Step outside to discover your own private paradise, where endless possibilities await. The expansive backyard offers plenty of space for outdoor entertaining, with a patio area perfect for al fresco dining and a serene yard with fruitful blueberry bushes and plum tree, providing the ideal backdrop for summer barbecues and garden parties. Conveniently located in the heart of Wetumpka, this home offers access to shopping, dining, and entertainment options, as well as top-rated schools and recreational facilities. With new shingles, hot water heater, & both interior & exterior A/C units installed within the last 3 years, this home offers some comfort & peace of mind. Don't miss your chance to make 76 Windsong Loop your own. Schedule a private tour today!!!!
